headline: Eggo速 Unveils Three New Protein Waffle and Pancake Flavors, Expanding Its Line with the Same Great Taste Fans Love
summary: Protein never tasted this good. Eggo速 is changing the breakfast game with an expanded lineup of protein waffles and pancakes that deliver the same delicious taste you know and love in every fluffy bite. As the only leading waffle brand with 20% of your recommended daily value of protein in every serving, Eggo proves you don't have to sacrifice taste to fuel your morning.
